    user[用户行为] --> collect[数据收集]
    collect --> extract[特征提取]
    extract --> profile[用户画像构建]
    
    knowledge[知识图谱] --> path[学习路径规划]
    profile --> path
    
    problems[题目库] --> recommend[智能题目推荐]
    path --> recommend
    
    submit[代码提交] --> analysis[代码智能分析]
    recommend --> analysis
    
    analysis --> feedback[学习反馈优化]
    feedback --> visual[学习进度可视化]
    
